
### 5. Package Configuration Files

#### `packages\database\package.json`
```json
{
  "name": "@miharina/database",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Miharina database schemas and migrations",
  "main": "index.js",
  "scripts": {
    "migrate": "node migrations/migrate.js",
    "seed": "node migrations/seed.js",
    "reset": "node migrations/reset.js"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "pg": "^8.11.0",
    "@databases/pg": "^5.4.1"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/pg": "^8.10.0"
  }
}